Component + Layout
https://beyondco.de/blog/blade-components-for-your-layout

Passing Data to Components
https://laravel.com/docs/11.x/blade#passing-data-to-components

Create component
php artisan make:component Alert
php artisan make:component forms.input --view

Create controller
php artisan make:controller User/NotificationController


Create migration
php artisan make:migration create_notification_table

Run migration
php artisan migrate

Create model
php artisan make:model Flight
php artisan make:model Flight --migration //create migration as well



Event
https://arjunamrutiya.medium.com/a-step-by-step-guide-to-laravel-events-and-listeners-with-examples-634d7a018fa0

php artisan make:event UserCreated
php artisan make:listener UserCreatedListner --event=UserCreated
